WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:45.451

00:01:36.140 --> 00:01:37.191
=The Company=
=Season 1=

00:01:37.215 --> 00:01:41.140
(Adapted from Xuan Se's novel
of the same title.)

00:01:41.260 --> 00:01:44.140
=Episode 9=

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:53.879
The young escort master of Qinghe
is back.

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:55.799
Just you today?

00:01:57.319 --> 00:01:58.480
The rest are worn out

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:59.239
and still resting.

00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:01.640
Two finely minced pork buns
and a bowl of rice congee.

00:02:01.720 --> 00:02:02.439
Thank you, madam.

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:02.920
Sure.

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:03.519
Please come in.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:11.719
Madam.

00:02:11.719 --> 00:02:12.520
Here you go.

00:02:12.919 --> 00:02:13.439
Sure.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:14.719
Come again.

00:02:14.719 --> 00:02:15.240
Alright.

00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:22.120
Let me take a look at that.

00:02:22.439 --> 00:02:22.960
Alright.

00:02:33.479 --> 00:02:34.159
Madam,

00:02:34.159 --> 00:02:35.360
I'll pay in full.

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.240
I'm not eating.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:37.280
Wait.

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:38.400
You're leaving like this?

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.599
Did you see clearly?

00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:43.000
That was Gu Bingyu?

00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:54.540
(Laifu Storehouse)

00:03:19.919 --> 00:03:20.680
Are we going in?

00:03:22.170 --> 00:03:23.830
This place is crowded,
and the routes are intricate.

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:25.080
Go check if there's a back door.

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:26.000
Got it.

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:32.879
Two bowls of tea.

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:33.840
Coming.

00:03:33.919 --> 00:03:34.719
Please sit.

00:03:39.800 --> 00:03:40.840
Here's your tea.

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:52.360
There's no back door.

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:53.400
Only one exit.

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:54.520
Has he come out yet?

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:08.919
It's broad daylight.

00:04:09.159 --> 00:04:10.560
What could take so long?

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:12.479
Should we go in and take a look?

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:19.040
Excuse me.

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:21.759
Which room is
Escort Gu Bingyu staying in?

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:23.120
Who are you?

00:04:23.759 --> 00:04:25.000
We're his friends.

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:26.720
We got separated and came to meet him.

00:04:27.519 --> 00:04:28.000
Gentlemen,

00:04:28.079 --> 00:04:28.920
follow me.

00:04:29.279 --> 00:04:29.879
Thank you.

00:04:30.010 --> 00:04:31.439
Take the stairs to the second floor.

00:04:31.439 --> 00:04:32.240
"Heaven" Room.

00:04:35.839 --> 00:04:36.680
Split up.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:09.120
No signs that the window was opened.

00:05:09.300 --> 00:05:10.600
No footprints on the sill either.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.519
He didn't leave through the window.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.920
You're good at this, huh?

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:15.920
I watched dramas too, okay?

00:05:51.040 --> 00:05:53.319
So, where did Gu Bingyu go?

00:05:55.439 --> 00:05:56.720
Have you seen a guest

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:57.639
about this tall?

00:05:57.959 --> 00:05:58.560
No.

00:05:58.600 --> 00:05:59.279
Long face.

00:06:00.279 --> 00:06:00.920
No.

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:01.959
Let's go.

00:06:06.820 --> 00:06:09.260
(Wedding Invitation,
Du Residence, Cangzhou)

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:12.680
Gu Bingyu!

00:06:14.199 --> 00:06:15.319
Gu Bingyu!

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:20.600
Why the rush, Pu?

00:06:20.759 --> 00:06:21.680
What happened?

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:24.920
Tell me honestly.

00:06:25.519 --> 00:06:26.480
Did Huaijin

00:06:27.839 --> 00:06:30.480
really die during the escort robbery
three years ago?

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:34.360
Of course.

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:36.720
I watched her...

00:06:39.199 --> 00:06:41.160
I watched her breathe her last
in my arms.

00:06:42.399 --> 00:06:43.839
How could that be fake?

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:52.040
I just...

00:06:54.199 --> 00:06:55.519
I just

00:06:57.879 --> 00:06:59.279
saw her in the city.

00:07:00.839 --> 00:07:01.639
Impossible.

00:07:03.400 --> 00:07:04.760
You must've mistaken someone else.

00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:08.480
No.

00:07:10.439 --> 00:07:11.879
I couldn't be wrong.

00:07:12.959 --> 00:07:15.639
I may forget anyone or anything,

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.839
but her face

00:07:19.079 --> 00:07:20.480
only grows clearer

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:24.279
with time.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:31.839
Pu,

00:07:34.519 --> 00:07:36.240
you should rest.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.439
Didn't the physician say

00:07:38.700 --> 00:07:41.319
love sickness made someone ill,
and accumulated worry became pain?

00:07:41.319 --> 00:07:42.680
That can cause hallucinations.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:43.639
If this continues,

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:45.439
I fear your inner demons
will overcome you.

00:07:45.439 --> 00:07:47.279
I told you I wasn't mistaken!

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:51.399
Why won't you believe me?

00:07:52.079 --> 00:07:53.480
You're her brother.

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:56.439
Don't you want her to still be alive?

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:02.160
Fine.

00:08:03.639 --> 00:08:04.879
If you don't believe me,

00:08:05.800 --> 00:08:07.680
let's go to Guangji Apothecary.

00:08:07.759 --> 00:08:09.000
She might pass by there again.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:09.399
Pu.

00:08:09.399 --> 00:08:10.199
Let's go find her.

00:08:10.199 --> 00:08:10.600
Pu.

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.920
Let's go now.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:14.199
Pu Jingtang, wake up!

00:08:19.759 --> 00:08:21.399
Gu Huaijin is dead.

00:08:24.614 --> 00:08:25.959
She's dead.

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:33.159
Please.

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:36.519
Forget her.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:39.919
No.

00:08:43.879 --> 00:08:45.360
I don't want to wake up.

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:50.919
Revive the Gu family

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:53.480
and restore its honor.

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:55.799
It's enough
that you alone stay clear-headed.

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:01.519
What am I?

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:12.639
I'm just a lodger who doesn't even
deserve to guard her grave.

00:09:19.759 --> 00:09:21.279
I can do nothing.

00:09:22.639 --> 00:09:24.120
Aside from mourning,

00:09:25.559 --> 00:09:30.200
all I can do is sit there every day,
playing sorrowful tunes that never end.

00:09:37.679 --> 00:09:41.559
Within it, there lives an ancient tune.

00:09:42.639 --> 00:09:46.120
Yet few today truly appreciate it.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:51.000
Sir, I would gladly play it,

00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:57.960
but would you care to listen?

00:10:00.759 --> 00:10:04.000
Sir, I would gladly play it,

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:14.399
but would you care to listen?

00:10:38.039 --> 00:10:38.840
Set off.

00:10:44.639 --> 00:10:47.120
I didn't see Mr. Gu at all.

00:11:19.320 --> 00:11:20.120
Gu Huaijin.

00:11:22.799 --> 00:11:24.360
You finally show yourself.

00:11:36.440 --> 00:11:37.879
Or should I call you

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:39.879
Gu Bingyu?

00:11:40.960 --> 00:11:41.679
You?

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:42.480
He?

00:11:42.600 --> 00:11:43.639
The same person?

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:46.799
Liuqing Comb can shift yin and yang.

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:49.240
You used it to turn into a man

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:50.879
to take your brother's place

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:52.759
and become
the head of the escort agency.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:54.500
I don't understand what you're saying.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:56.990
At the inn earlier today,

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:59.799
you changed from a man into a woman.

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:01.960
I didn't notice at first.

00:12:02.039 --> 00:12:04.879
Not until I found an empty cloth bundle
in the room.

00:12:06.039 --> 00:12:07.399
What used to be inside

00:12:08.279 --> 00:12:10.000
should've been women's clothes, right?

00:12:12.799 --> 00:12:15.399
You think you can identify me
just by a bundle?

00:12:15.759 --> 00:12:19.279
The butler at the Gu Residence
would recognize you.

00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:20.840
You were afraid he saw you,

00:12:20.919 --> 00:12:22.679
so you waited
until the escort team left,

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:25.159
then secretly returned
to Gu Bingyu's room.

00:12:25.399 --> 00:12:27.120
Shall I call him over to confirm it?

00:12:27.279 --> 00:12:27.879
Shut up.

00:12:28.360 --> 00:12:29.200
Who are you, really?

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:30.759
Miss, let's talk calmly.

00:12:30.879 --> 00:12:32.320
You're not a ruthless person.

00:12:32.559 --> 00:12:33.679
And we mean no harm.

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:36.320
This Liuqing Comb belonged
to a friend of mine.

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:38.519
He was caught in a family struggle

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:39.799
and died in a fire.

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.840
His home was burned to ruins,

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:43.639
and many heirlooms

00:12:43.879 --> 00:12:45.879
were lost in the fire.

00:12:46.759 --> 00:12:48.480
The reason we've been searching for you

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:50.600
is only to take Liuqing Comb back.

00:12:59.039 --> 00:12:59.879
I see.

00:13:00.879 --> 00:13:02.279
You also carry a feud.

00:13:03.399 --> 00:13:05.559
You want to help your friend
restore his family.

00:13:09.860 --> 00:13:13.180
(Memorial Tablet of
the Late Brother Gu Bingyu)

00:13:45.919 --> 00:13:46.720
Bingyu!

00:13:56.159 --> 00:13:56.840
Watch out!

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:01.639
Bingyu!

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.120
Bingyu.

00:14:28.639 --> 00:14:29.440
Bingyu.

00:14:30.080 --> 00:14:30.879
Bingyu.

00:14:33.879 --> 00:14:34.679
Bingyu.

00:14:35.159 --> 00:14:36.000
Bingyu.

00:14:36.399 --> 00:14:37.240
Huaijin.

00:14:38.360 --> 00:14:39.159
Bingyu.

00:14:47.159 --> 00:14:48.200
This comb

00:14:49.559 --> 00:14:51.559
is called Liuqing.

00:14:52.759 --> 00:14:55.639
I got it from a stranger.

00:14:57.759 --> 00:14:59.200
Legend has it that

00:15:00.879 --> 00:15:02.320
this comb can turn yin into yang

00:15:02.639 --> 00:15:04.120
and yang into yin.

00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:07.080
It once helped a woman

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:10.399
to become a general on the battlefield.

00:15:15.279 --> 00:15:16.120
Huaijin.

00:15:20.200 --> 00:15:22.120
Why are all the men
so foolish and incompetent,

00:15:23.720 --> 00:15:25.519
no match for a woman like Tiying?

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:27.320
Remember.

00:15:30.519 --> 00:15:32.480
Protect the Gu's clear reputation.

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:37.759
You can do it.

00:15:40.759 --> 00:15:42.039
Bingyu.

00:15:42.759 --> 00:15:44.399
Bingyu, don't die.

00:15:44.559 --> 00:15:45.440
Bingyu.

00:15:45.919 --> 00:15:47.000
Bingyu.

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:48.919
Bingyu.

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:55.679
Bingyu.

00:17:17.200 --> 00:17:19.960
You're such a remarkable woman.

00:17:20.519 --> 00:17:22.279
Heaven never lets the persistent down.

00:17:22.480 --> 00:17:25.599
I've finally found the mastermind
behind the escort robbery back then.

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:29.240
Since we're in the same situation,

00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:31.359
could you return the comb

00:17:31.640 --> 00:17:32.799
to us?

00:17:40.839 --> 00:17:41.640
Please forgive me.

00:17:41.700 --> 00:17:43.039
I still have an unfinished matter.

00:17:43.319 --> 00:17:44.759
Please stay here for now.

00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:46.680
I still need Liuqing Comb.

00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:47.759
Once it's done,

00:17:47.759 --> 00:17:49.519
I may personally return it to you.

00:17:49.599 --> 00:17:50.400
My apologies.

00:18:11.720 --> 00:18:13.960
She speaks politely,

00:18:14.200 --> 00:18:15.960
but she fights without mercy.

00:18:16.039 --> 00:18:17.680
That unfinished matter

00:18:18.279 --> 00:18:20.160
must be taking revenge on her enemy.

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:20.880
Enough talk.

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:22.150
Let's get out of here first.

00:18:24.839 --> 00:18:26.039
She locked the door.

00:18:30.440 --> 00:18:31.880
The window won't open either.

00:18:32.079 --> 00:18:33.759
Could there be a secret passage?

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:41.319
Have you seen a guest

00:18:41.319 --> 00:18:42.240
about this tall?

00:18:42.519 --> 00:18:43.400
No.

00:18:43.559 --> 00:18:44.359
Long face.

00:18:47.420 --> 00:18:50.519
(Wedding Invitation,
Du Residence, Cangzhou)

00:18:50.519 --> 00:18:51.200
Stop looking.

00:18:51.519 --> 00:18:52.599
I know where she's going.

00:18:52.599 --> 00:18:53.079
Where?

00:18:54.359 --> 00:18:55.599
Cangzhou.

00:18:56.039 --> 00:18:57.759
We can't even get out of here. Cangzhou?

00:19:16.319 --> 00:19:17.200
Let's go.

00:19:20.200 --> 00:19:20.960
Where to?

00:19:21.319 --> 00:19:22.440
The Du Residence.

00:19:22.440 --> 00:19:25.180
(Du Residence)

00:19:41.820 --> 00:19:43.759
(Du Wenhua, former Governor of Cangzhou)

00:19:43.759 --> 00:19:44.680
My Lord,

00:19:45.079 --> 00:19:47.160
the ginseng soup has been tasted.

00:19:47.480 --> 00:19:48.279
Also,

00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:50.599
Master Du is requesting an audience.

00:19:52.920 --> 00:19:53.960
Let him in.

00:19:58.940 --> 00:20:00.820
(Grand Coordinator,
adopted son of Du Wenhua)

00:20:02.039 --> 00:20:02.920
Father.

00:20:05.319 --> 00:20:06.079
Well,

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:08.359
it's so early.

00:20:08.880 --> 00:20:10.119
What's the matter?

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:12.880
The wedding arrangements

00:20:13.799 --> 00:20:15.480
are nearly complete.

00:20:16.240 --> 00:20:17.519
Everyone in the family

00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:19.279
hopes

00:20:19.759 --> 00:20:21.359
you'll take the seat of honor.

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:24.839
Lian is the descendant of the Du family

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:27.079
and your only grandson.

00:20:27.759 --> 00:20:28.759
He wishes

00:20:30.440 --> 00:20:32.519
to offer you a cup of gratitude tea.

00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:34.559
This soup

00:20:36.440 --> 00:20:37.359
is unclean.

00:20:45.359 --> 00:20:46.559
You want me

00:20:47.759 --> 00:20:50.200
to step out that door.

00:20:51.359 --> 00:20:53.200
But you know it yourself.

00:20:53.880 --> 00:20:57.640
Morality and filial duty

00:20:58.519 --> 00:20:59.880
mean nothing to me.

00:21:00.680 --> 00:21:01.960
Since leaving the palace,

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:06.480
you've been my adopted son
for over forty years.

00:21:07.240 --> 00:21:08.920
Have we ever eaten

00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:13.279
at the same table?

00:21:15.079 --> 00:21:18.279
I've lived so cautiously all my life.

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:20.960
Why should I break the habit

00:21:22.640 --> 00:21:24.400
now?

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:29.559
Father,

00:21:29.839 --> 00:21:31.720
I've followed you for many years.

00:21:32.519 --> 00:21:35.119
My loyalty is carved into my bones.

00:21:35.720 --> 00:21:37.920
I truly hope you'll see

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:39.380
the Du family prosper

00:21:39.390 --> 00:21:41.240
with all the generations
united under one roof.

00:21:49.599 --> 00:21:50.400
Father,

00:21:50.839 --> 00:21:52.680
you're the true master of the Du family.

00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:54.440
No matter

00:21:54.640 --> 00:21:56.319
how high I rise,

00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:59.359
I'll never reach
even a slight fraction of

00:22:00.960 --> 00:22:03.039
your standing at court.

00:22:11.640 --> 00:22:12.759
Stop.

00:22:26.279 --> 00:22:27.799
I'll drink it now.

00:22:28.599 --> 00:22:29.440
It's clean now.

00:22:34.039 --> 00:22:35.519
Please come in.

00:22:35.740 --> 00:22:37.839
(Du Residence)

00:22:37.839 --> 00:22:38.759
Please come in.

00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:17.519
Did you find anything?

00:23:17.519 --> 00:23:18.279
Yes.

00:23:18.440 --> 00:23:19.599
There's a lot of food today.

00:23:19.799 --> 00:23:21.240
This is especially good. Try it.

00:23:23.720 --> 00:23:25.119
And you?

00:23:26.359 --> 00:23:28.240
Did you see that chubby man
carrying two blades?

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:31.319
Steady steps.

00:23:31.599 --> 00:23:32.720
And that tall one.

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:34.440
His fists are bigger than your face.

00:23:34.960 --> 00:23:35.799
That's normal.

00:23:35.799 --> 00:23:36.680
My face is small.

00:23:37.390 --> 00:23:39.759
And that red-clad woman.
Her face is full of killing intent.

00:23:40.240 --> 00:23:42.319
That short one.
His qinggong is impressive.

00:23:42.900 --> 00:23:44.119
Every one of them is a master.

00:23:44.279 --> 00:23:46.279
Have you ever seen a wedding

00:23:46.279 --> 00:23:47.640
with this many experts?

00:23:48.200 --> 00:23:49.200
Looks like

00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:52.559
today's wedding banquet
is anything but ordinary.

00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:56.240
Old Master Du has arrived!

00:23:58.079 --> 00:23:58.980
Please watch your step.

00:24:00.240 --> 00:24:01.039
Careful.

00:24:03.200 --> 00:24:06.000
- Congratulations, Old Master Du.
- Congratulations, Old Master Du.

00:24:09.440 --> 00:24:11.039
On this auspicious day,

00:24:11.279 --> 00:24:13.279
the Du Residence celebrates great joy.

00:24:13.799 --> 00:24:17.119
Perform the dance and bring blessings.

00:24:18.680 --> 00:24:19.400
Father, look.

00:24:19.640 --> 00:24:20.960
I invited them.

00:24:23.279 --> 00:24:24.440
What's that?

00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:25.960
This is Nuo dance.

00:24:26.400 --> 00:24:27.880
It's to ward off evil and disease

00:24:28.200 --> 00:24:29.319
and summon good fortune.

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:31.480
They're rich indeed.

00:25:14.200 --> 00:25:17.000
It's said the Nuo dance
can quell dark spirits.

00:25:17.279 --> 00:25:19.000
All demons

00:25:20.160 --> 00:25:22.000
have fled in fear.

