using my brother's identity anymore.

00:35:31.280 --> 00:35:34.360
I don't know what will become
of the Gu Escort Agency,

00:35:35.239 --> 00:35:36.760
but it's time to face reality.

00:35:37.560 --> 00:35:39.200
"One shouldn't fear the changes
under heaven.

00:35:39.210 --> 00:35:40.850
One shouldn't blindly follow
ancestral rules.

00:35:40.860 --> 00:35:42.490
One shouldn't be deterred
by complaints of others."

00:35:44.719 --> 00:35:46.079
This is what Jingtang taught me.

00:35:49.280 --> 00:35:50.079
Miss Gu,

00:35:51.639 --> 00:35:52.960
I want to tell you something.

00:35:54.199 --> 00:35:55.079
In the future,

00:35:55.960 --> 00:35:58.360
women can achieve great things

00:35:59.280 --> 00:36:01.400
and shoulder
great responsibilities like men.

00:36:01.960 --> 00:36:03.599
You don't have to become someone's wife

00:36:04.519 --> 00:36:06.000
to live freely

00:36:06.480 --> 00:36:07.119
and openly.

00:36:09.280 --> 00:36:10.280
Really?

00:36:12.400 --> 00:36:13.440
That would be wonderful.

00:36:22.639 --> 00:36:23.239
Take care.

00:36:23.519 --> 00:36:24.119
You too.

