00:37:46.039 --> 00:37:48.559
if Miss Gu inherited
the family business,

00:37:48.960 --> 00:37:50.000
get married,

00:37:50.079 --> 00:37:51.519
or become a nun?

00:37:52.519 --> 00:37:54.239
