00:38:01.920 --> 00:38:03.199
I need an ending.

00:38:04.079 --> 00:38:04.800
Alright.

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:06.360
How about this?

00:38:07.920 --> 00:38:09.159
From then on,

00:38:09.400 --> 00:38:12.519
